=head1 NAME

_FIX_EXTRA_HEADERS_ - Instrument specific initialisation

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is the CGS4 specific _FIX_EXTRA_HEADERS_

All it does is hardwire the ORAC_OBSERVATIONS_MODE user-header to
"spectroscopy".

=head1 TASKS

None.

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

None

=head1 AUTHOR

Paul Hirst <p.hirst@jach.hawaii.edu>

=cut

$Frm->uhdr("ORAC_OBSERVATION_MODE", "spectroscopy");